{"title":"青藏旅吟","authors":["玛拉沁夫"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"青藏旅吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玛拉沁夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青海湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青海湖边宿帐篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连宵月下又驼铃；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡笳不奏离人怨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪卷金戈铁马声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花甲壮游兴似童，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崔嵬青藏千里行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风云如海匆匆渡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷暖起伏一笑中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月牙泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秦时明月汉时关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐宋风流汇雪山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙韵奇情何处觅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敦煌怀里月牙泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落日归山月照东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千峰万岭入朦胧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京城学子寻诗客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉卧沙泉梦黎明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐古拉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐古拉口五千三，①"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪封季夏碧天寒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人至此处羞言老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再试珠峰万仞巅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立马昆仑数雪峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收鞭那曲薄冰行；②"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当雄一过平川路，③"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥见辉煌日光城。④"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：①唐古拉山口海拔５３００米。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②那曲：西藏地名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"③当雄：西藏地名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"④日光城：即拉萨。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}